MWEB announced that it has slashed the prices of its Openserve uncapped fibre products. The discounted prices will be available to both new and existing customers, and include free installation, connection, and a router. The company also announced that it has removed all throttling from its Openserve fibre products, granting customers a better fibre experience. “MWEB have not throttled Vumatel, Frogfoot, or Octotel Fibre products for some time now, but from 1 September, Openserve Fibre will be added to this list,” said Mweb. The new prices of Openserve uncapped fibre packages available from MWEB are listed below.